text:
using if statements should do the trick, for example:

```&lt;div class="testimonial__details"&gt;
	&lt;span class="testimonial__full-name"&gt;{{ module.full_name }}&lt;/span&gt;
	{% if module.title %}&lt;span class="testimonial__title"&gt;, {{ module.title }}&lt;/span&gt;{% endif %}
	{% if module.company %}&lt;span class="testimonial__company"&gt;, {{ module.company }}&lt;/span&gt;{% endif %}
&lt;/div&gt;```
